<br />
Quick note: Though you might be tempted to buy Mines of Moria, as it seeems there are a fair few cards here from that set, I’d not reccomend it. It’s widely considered the worst set yet, and most of the owerful rares have banned (O Elbereth, Flaming Brand) or rendered useless (Tower assassin, Secret Sentinels) for standard play, thus decreasing thier value. Maybe a couple boosters, plus the two starters if no one is willing to give you thier Gandalfs. Seee if people can donate Tidings of Erebor for instance, it’s not a heavily played card and Mines isn’t very popular, so people might have extra’s floating around.<br />
